  "texts": [
    "The simulation setup also raises some questions, according to NDN policy, MATLAB is not a suitable simulator.",
    "Kapetanidou and Tsaoussidis (2022) proposed a CPA prevention scheme for NDN using the reputation-based model.",
    "According to this model, the content source is given a reputation based on the feedback of previous travel.",
    "If the feedback of the previous travel is positive the content will be considered non-poisoned and suggested to send the requested users.",
    "To define the reputation ratio, authors define a metric named Notoriety which shows the number of poison contents."
  ],
